name: HPPR SYNDICATE
description: The HPPR Syndicate is the place to be.  As an abandoned warehouse office turned stomping ground, this place is the central hub for Hoppers to mingle, plan, and organize.  The PC terminal keeps track of all items logged as inventory and is a way to archive any loot Hoppers have acquired on their missions.  As the Hopper crew expands, so will the HPPR Syndicate - we can expect some major renovations in the future!
